 }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15738878\charrsid15738878 Just going back to the 19th century, British pure mathematics, some of it was in a very bad state \endash  far behind the French and Germans 
