Applied mathematics, the great mathematical physicists, Maxwell and Kelvin and so forth, applied mathematics was very strong, and the way applied mathematicians and pure mathematicians approached problems is different.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
