\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid16597392  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15738878\charrsid15738878 
Now, I approached statistics, I think, as a form of applied mathematics, which, of course, in one sense it obviously is.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid16597392  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15738878\charrsid15738878 But on the other hand, the methods \endash  the mathematical methods \endash  that you use, are different.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
