m talking about people at the very theoretical end of the subject \endash  tend to be more like pure mathematicians than applied mathematicians.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f40\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid16597392  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
